videos.description: Jamaree Bouyea makes a nice pass inside to Damari Milstead, who tosses it out to Dzmitry Ryuny for the three-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bouyea's nice pass sets up San Francisco's 3) 2020/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bouyea's nice pass sets up San Francisco's 3

videos.description: Khalil Shabazz uses good footwork to fool the defenders, hitting a step-back three-pointer.

videos.description: Virginia tosses the ball around, making its way to Tomas Woldetensae, who hits a 3-pointer from the top of the key to give the Cavaliers a 3-point lead.
